      • getAggregations

        public List<Aggregation> getAggregations(Map<String,Class> nameToTypeMap)
        Parameters:
        nameToTypeMap - a map of aggNames to their expected type (extension of Aggregation class)
        Returns:
        A list of aggregation objects for the provided name:type pairs if the name can be found in the root json object
        Throws:
        RuntimeException - if no constructor found for an expected type in the map

      • getAggregation

        public <T extends Aggregation> T getAggregation(String aggName,
                                       Class<T> aggType)
        Parameters:
        aggName - Name of the desired aggregation
        aggType - Extension of Aggregation class expected as return type
        Returns:
        Aggregation of type T if aggName can be found in aggregation json or null otherwise
        Throws:
        RuntimeException - if no constructor exists for provided aggType
